<l>aṟattā ṟituveṉa vēṇṭā civikai</l>
<l>poṟuttāṉō ṭūrntā ṉiṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>No need to spell it out—that this is dharma's way—about him</l>
<l>who bore the palanquin and him who rode it.</l>
